*& Custom Table Definitions for RVO Weekly Filing
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Table 1: ZMM_RVO_PB   - Parboiled Rice CN/HSN Codes
*& Table 2: ZMM_RVO_NPB  - Non-Parboiled Rice CN/HSN Codes
*&
*& Purpose: Maintain CN codes to classify materials as Parboiled or
*&          Non-Parboiled for RVO filing. This avoids hardcoding CN
*&          codes in the report program ZMM_RVOREP.
