*======================================================================*
* TABLE 1: ZMM_RVO_PB (Parboiled Rice CN Codes)
*======================================================================*
* SE11 → Create Table → ZMM_RVO_PB
*
* Short Description: CN/HSN Codes for Parboiled Rice (RVO Filing)
* Delivery Class: C (Customizing table, maintenance only by customer)
* Data Browser/Table View Maint: Display/Maintenance Allowed
*
* Fields:
* -------
* Field Name     Key  Data Element   Type      Length  Description
* -------------- ---  -------------- --------- ------  ----------------------------
* MANDT          X    MANDT          CLNT      3       Client
* STEUC          X    STEUC          CHAR      16      Control Code (CN/HSN Code)
* DESCRIPTION         TEXT40         CHAR      40      Description of CN Code
* ERNAM               ERNAM          CHAR      12      Created By
* ERDAT               ERDAT          DATS      8       Created On
* AENAM               AENAM          CHAR      12      Changed By
* AEDAT               AEDAT          DATS      8       Changed On
*
* Technical Settings (SE11 → Technical Settings):
*   Data Class       : APPL0 (Master data, transparent table)
*   Size Category    : 0 (0 to 2,200 records)
*   Buffering        : Buffering Switched On
*   Buffering Type   : Fully Buffered
*   Logging          : Not Required
*
* Table Maintenance Generator (SE11 → Utilities → Table Maint. Gen.):
*   Authorization Group: &NC&
*   Function Group     : ZMM_RVO_PB
*   Maintenance Type   : One Step (Overview screen only)
*   Maintenance Screen : 0001 (Screen Number)
*   Overview Screen    : Generate default
*
* Initial Data Entry (SM30 → ZMM_RVO_PB):
*   STEUC = 1006306792 | DESCRIPTION = Parboiled Milled Rice
*
*======================================================================*

*======================================================================*
* TABLE 2: ZMM_RVO_NPB (Non-Parboiled Rice CN Codes)
*======================================================================*
* SE11 → Create Table → ZMM_RVO_NPB
*
* Short Description: CN/HSN Codes for Non-Parboiled Rice (RVO Filing)
* Delivery Class: C (Customizing table, maintenance only by customer)
* Data Browser/Table View Maint: Display/Maintenance Allowed
*
* Fields:
* -------
* Field Name     Key  Data Element   Type      Length  Description
* -------------- ---  -------------- --------- ------  ----------------------------
* MANDT          X    MANDT          CLNT      3       Client
* STEUC          X    STEUC          CHAR      16      Control Code (CN/HSN Code)
* MATCH_TYPE          ZMATCH_TYPE    CHAR      1       Match Type (E=Exact, P=Prefix)
* DESCRIPTION         TEXT40         CHAR      40      Description of CN Code
* ERNAM               ERNAM          CHAR      12      Created By
* ERDAT               ERDAT          DATS      8       Created On
* AENAM               AENAM          CHAR      12      Changed By
* AEDAT               AEDAT          DATS      8       Changed On
*
* Technical Settings (SE11 → Technical Settings):
*   Data Class       : APPL0 (Master data, transparent table)
*   Size Category    : 0 (0 to 2,200 records)
*   Buffering        : Buffering Switched On
*   Buffering Type   : Fully Buffered
*   Logging          : Not Required
*
* Table Maintenance Generator (SE11 → Utilities → Table Maint. Gen.):
*   Authorization Group: &NC&
*   Function Group     : ZMM_RVO_NPB
*   Maintenance Type   : One Step (Overview screen only)
*   Maintenance Screen : 0001 (Screen Number)
*   Overview Screen    : Generate default
*
* MATCH_TYPE field explanation:
*   'E' = Exact match  → STEUC must match exactly
*   'P' = Prefix match → STEUC value is used as a prefix (starts with)
*
* This is needed because as per the spec, Non-Parboiled codes are
* identified by PREFIX (starts with 10063098, 10063094), while
* Parboiled is an exact match (1006306792).
*
* Initial Data Entry (SM30 → ZMM_RVO_NPB):
*   STEUC = 10063098 | MATCH_TYPE = P | DESCRIPTION = Non-Parboiled Milled Rice (98)
*   STEUC = 10063094 | MATCH_TYPE = P | DESCRIPTION = Non-Parboiled Milled Rice (94)
*
*======================================================================*

*======================================================================*
* DATA ELEMENT: ZMATCH_TYPE (if not reusing an existing one)
*======================================================================*
* SE11 → Create Data Element → ZMATCH_TYPE
*
* Short Description: Match Type for CN Code Comparison
* Domain           : Create domain ZMATCH_TYPE
*   Data Type      : CHAR
*   Length         : 1
*   Fixed Values   :
*     'E' = Exact Match
*     'P' = Prefix Match
