*& Description : Fetches GRN data against POs of type ZEUL for a given
*&               week, classifies materials as Parboiled/Non-Parboiled
*&               based on CN codes (from custom tables ZMM_RVO_PB and
*&               ZMM_RVO_NPB), calculates quantities and values in EUR
*&               for RVO weekly filing automation.
